{"tid":1895932,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】世衛忽然澄清︰不再用「大流行病」分類, 即係所有保險將會無得賠!!!","createTime":"2020-02-24T23:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T11:14:35.000Z","uid":88743,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1341840a93891a1e42132c5fe3853d050332ffb0","tid":1895932,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:03:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/【武漢肺炎】世衛忽然澄清︰不再用「大流行病」分類-208640\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B%E5%BF%BD%E7%84%B6%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85%EF%B8%B0%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E7%94%A8%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%8C%E7%97%85%E3%80%8D%E5%88%86%E9%A1%9E-208640&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwbTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=a69f9f98\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/【武漢肺炎】世衛忽然澄清︰不再用「大流行病」分類-208640</a><br />\n世界衛生組織近期曾表明，新型冠狀病毒肺炎仍然未算是「大流行病」(pandemic、即在全球廣泛傳播的新疾病)，週一卻忽然「澄清」，稱其實世衛已不再使用「大流行病」這個分類。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">世衛發言人亞沙雷維奇(Tarik Jasarevic)表示︰「已經沒有(大流行病)這個官方分類」(there is no official category)</span></strong>，並稱「世衛不再使用有些人由09年起聽慣的分級制度，世衛已按《國際衛生條例》，宣佈(新冠肺炎)疫情是『國際關注的突發公共衛生事件』。」<br />\n<br />\n世衛表明已沒有再用「大流行病」一詞，事出突然，其中世衛傳染病災害管理部門主管布萊恩德(Sylvie Briand)，月初時還說疫情「並非在大流行病狀態」(We are not in a pandemic)，而只是「有多個疫源地的流行病」(an epidemic with &quot;multiple foci&quot;)，沒有提及已停用「大流行病」分類。<br />\n<br />\n路透社指，世衛09年時曾宣佈H1N1豬流感是「大流行病」，令藥廠爭相研發疫苗及藥物，最終疫情沒有預期般嚴重，令世衛捱轟。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味唔知收左保險公司幾多錢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856223bf22e7355f50d85960d6a5c6e71c4a57d5","tid":1895932,"uid":12612,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:05:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"972987d4864939426cd0ed5ca6d76ef57c2473eb","tid":1895932,"uid":88743,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"856223bf22e7355f50d85960d6a5c6e71c4a57d5","tid":1895932,"uid":12612,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:05:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:06:32.000Z","msg":"唔識"},{"pid":"14184153a947dfa3bb594aca3cb1a90a1af36e95","tid":1895932,"uid":38633,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:09:17.000Z","msg":"世衛正仆街, 講完"},{"pid":"0b707c65fd7d3d5a317f40ab1b4fb83fe5e77028","tid":1895932,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:20:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每日全球武汉肺炎新闻</span>（中文字幕）<br />\n<a href=\"https://livestream.com/accounts/27235681/events/8197481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flivestream.com%2Faccounts%2F27235681%2Fevents%2F8197481&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwbTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=013fb930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://livestream.com/accounts/27235681/events/8197481</a>"},{"pid":"cad21a7f0891596b64c742027608af2c1cf53d55","tid":1895932,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"14184153a947dfa3bb594aca3cb1a90a1af36e95","tid":1895932,"uid":38633,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:09:17.000Z","msg":"世衛正仆街, 講完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T10:58:29.000Z","msg":"真係好撚仆街..."},{"pid":"caf26f968210ebe35a4885fddd98281c38a3f39d","tid":1895932,"uid":154784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1341840a93891a1e42132c5fe3853d050332ffb0","tid":1895932,"uid":8